oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmy Newman and Dave Dudley (undated)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Newman, Jimmy C.; Dudley, Dave; Smith, Sammi; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Jimmy Newman, Dave Dudley, Sammi Smith, Earl Richards and Red and Fred. Poster is an undated template and features metal photoplates of Jimmy Newman, Dave Dudley, Sammi Smith, and Earl Richards.
